library(dplyr)
library(tidyr) 
library(splines)
j1 = read_xlsx("jobdata.xlsx")
j22 <- j1[,-5:-17]

j22 <- data.frame(j22)

j33 <- j22 %>% gather("item",value,3:4) %>% 
  bind_cols(data.frame(item_id=rep(1:2,each=6))) #tidyrdplyr

ggplot(j33,aes(x=,value))+
  geom_bar(aes(fill=item),stat = "identity",position="dodge",width=0.8)+
  labs(title="",y = "") + scale_x_continuous(breaks=seq(101,105,by=2))
